      <title>Revolut 首席执行官在 8 月份出售了价值约 2.5 亿美元的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/revolut-ceo-offloaded-about-250-million-in-august-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Revolut Ltd. 的首席执行官尼克·斯托隆斯基 (Nik Storonsky) 在上个月的二次股票发售中出售了其持有的价值约 2.5 亿美元的公司股份，此次发售对该公司的估值达到 450 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/revolut-ceo-offloaded-about-250-million-in-august-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:44:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德称欧元区经济增长风险偏向下行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/ecb-s-lagarde-says-growth-risks-tilted-to-downside-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧元区经济增长风险“偏向下行”。她在法兰克福举行的新闻发布会上发表了上述言论。此前，央行决策者今年第二次下调利率，通胀率回落至 2%。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-12/ecb-s-lagarde-says-growth-risks-tilted-to-downside-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 13:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫斯科和基辅称俄罗斯军队正在库尔斯克发动进攻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/zelenskiy-says-russian-kursk-pushback-matches-ukraine-s-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰和俄罗斯表示，克里姆林宫已在俄罗斯库尔斯克边境地区开始反攻，试图击退自二战以来首次对其领土的军事入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/zelenskiy-says-russian-kursk-pushback-matches-ukraine-s-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 12:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息和美国公投将对美元造成怎样的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/from-fed-to-elections-fx-turbulence-buffets-dollar-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统辩论和关键通胀数据令市场预期年底前波动性将加剧，所有迹象都表明，对于预测美元走势的投资者来说，未来几个月将面临艰难的时期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/from-fed-to-elections-fx-turbulence-buffets-dollar-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦降息以刺激通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/pakistan-cuts-rates-to-revive-recovery-as-inflation-cools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀放缓为政策制定者恢复经济增长提供了空间，巴基斯坦连续第三次下调基准利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/pakistan-cuts-rates-to-revive-recovery-as-inflation-cools</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:56:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>销售前景令人失望，研发预算削减，Moderna 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/moderna-slashes-research-budget-as-vaccine-sales-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫德纳公司 (Moderna Inc.) 表示，在疫苗销售表现不佳后，该公司试图找到盈利之路，计划在未来三年内削减约 20% 的研发预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/moderna-slashes-research-budget-as-vaccine-sales-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行如预期降息，欧洲股市缩减涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/european-stocks-set-to-gain-ahead-of-ecb-interest-rate-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行在宣布符合预期的降息举措后，并未承诺采取具体的借贷成本路径，欧洲股市小幅缩减涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/european-stocks-set-to-gain-ahead-of-ecb-interest-rate-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 05:53:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据增强美联储降息预期，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/gold-holds-drop-as-inflation-data-douse-hopes-for-big-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国通胀数据再次快于预期，且失业救济申请人数增加，证实了美联储将在下周降息的预期，黄金价格攀升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/gold-holds-drop-as-inflation-data-douse-hopes-for-big-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:53:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储在 PPI 数据公布后押注稳定，股市波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀数据再次快于预期，但并未改变人们对美联储降息的预期，股市出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:27:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房东面临 1.5 万亿美元的商业房地产到期障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/landlords-face-a-1-5-trillion-commercial-real-estate-maturity-wall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据仲量联行称，到明年年底，写字楼、公寓大楼和其他商业地产的业主将有 1.5 万亿美元的债务到期。这意味着所欠金额和可用于再融资的资本之间的缺口高达 4000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/landlords-face-a-1-5-trillion-commercial-real-estate-maturity-wall</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
